{"title":"Wolf Tooth Ripsaw Aluminum Pedals","link":"https://theradavist.com/wolf-tooth-ripsaw-aluminum-pedals/","date":1712849244000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2570\" height=\"1712\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_6.jpg?fit=1200,1712&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_6.jpg?w=2570&amp;quality=75 2570w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_6.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_6.jpg?resize=2000,1332&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_6.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_6.jpg?resize=1536,1023&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_6.jpg?resize=2048,1364&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Wolf Tooth announced the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fproducts%2Fripsaw-aluminum-pedals\" target=\"_blank\">Ripsaw aluminum pedals</a> ($199.95) today. These feature a tapered platform, twelve pins per side, and are repairable. Letâ€™s check them out.<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/RipsawWolfTooth.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/RipsawWolfTooth.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/RipsawWolfTooth.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/RipsawWolfTooth.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/RipsawWolfTooth.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/RipsawWolfTooth.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/RipsawWolfTooth.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Wolf Tooth Ripsaw Aluminum Pedals feature a slim, lightweight design with a slight convex profile. The large, asymmetric machined aluminum platform provides strong foot support for all-mountain riding, while the thin convex profile is just 7mm thick at the leading edge. Inside the pedal are three fully sealed cartridge bearings, a stainless steel axle, a igus bushing, and a custom radial seal to protect internal components against trail debris.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_1.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_1.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_1.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/ripsaw-Section_1.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Ripsaw pedals are 12.5mm thick in the center and just 7mm thick in the front and rear edges. This profile is supportive and comfortable for all riders, while performing exceptionally well for riders who prefer pedaling with a mid-foot position or for shoes that do not have much structure or support.</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fproducts%2Fripsaw-aluminum-pedals\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/wolf-tooth-ripsaw-aluminum-pedals/\">Wolf Tooth Ripsaw Aluminum Pedals</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"b3abe4c60dd0189a40025a985385cc2e199dbdc19403f71f05faa8101576cefd","category":"Cycling"}